title: Statement by the Press Secretary on S. 1568 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
June 15, 2015

 



Statement by the Press Secretary on S. 1568





	On Monday, June 15, 2015, the President signed into law:

	S. 1568, which extends authorization of a Department of Veterans Affairs medical facility project in Denver, Colorado, and authorizes the transfer of amounts from other accounts to fund the project.
